refdb-elisp README
==================

This package contains two extensions for the Emacs editor:

refdb-mode.el adds an interface to RefDB, a reference database and
bibliography tool, see http://refdb.sourceforge.net.

ris.el adds editing support for RIS files.

See the enclosed documentation in HTML or PDF format for further
information.

To install the package on Unix-like systems, run:

tar -xzf refdb-elisp-1.0.tar.gz
cd refdb-elisp-1.0
./configure
make
make install

Add the following to your ~/.emacs (check the path on your system):

(load-file "/usr/local/etc/refdb-mode-config.el")

To install the package on Windows, please see the additional
instructions in the enclosed manual.

